<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>

<para>A <tag>transform</tag> specifies a mechanism for converting one format into
another during the assembly process. For example, if a <tag>module</tag> identifies
a resource in a foreign grammar, then a <tag>transform</tag> can be used to identify
the transformation that will convert the foreign grammar into DocBook.</para>

